{"title":"Paper. Guía hierro EV-2025-1","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Hematología/Paper. Guía hierro EV-2025-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Guía Consenso\\NHierro Intravenoso\\N(IV)","guid":"OxgxlSbO9_FLoN_mr-bxfA","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"## 1. Introducción y\\NAntecedentes","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"* Importancia: Tratamiento esencial ID / IDA.","guid":"uEg8ozh-11Oo7oA_xYe9kg","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"* Formulaciones\\NNuevas (TDI):","guid":"gTSmAO--7nvtHyhIugakwQ","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"* Ventajas: 1 visita (15-60 min), menos reacciones, sin toxicidad añadida.","guid":"u1qq5fhicb3weRmUjNfKpw","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"3","text":"* Reacciones:","guid":"nN2SksfEeaKw1-M99ALOxw","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"* Común: CARPA / Reacción Fishbane (pseudoalergia, no IgE).","guid":"P5htOtsL1e1yh4d3O1Yo4Q","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"5","text":"* Rara: Anafilaxia (<1:200,000).","guid":"qdvfcL0IHX908o8AD8k6LA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"1","text":"* Objetivo Guía: Prácticas seguras administración, manejo reacciones y TE-HP.","guid":"eJVxKfkJJqMG77LIUMh_3A","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"1","text":"* Método: Consenso Delphi (Expertos).","guid":"Yn2ku6dR5yPZdNzPkB-gMw","children":[]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"0","text":"## 2. Formulaciones\\NHierro IV","guid":"znp0wRXAo8Dbn-csASOGBQ","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"* **Recomendación General:** Preferir TDI sobre dosis múltiples.","guid":"BpyMsuFruNzybWZWpzf06A","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"10","text":"* **Formulaciones TDI (≥1000 mg / 15-60 min):**","guid":"IAuaeFmBAmil_TUtiq1uiA","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"10","text":"* **Óptimas:**","guid":"lwqh4wla4nYJ0K8VKrF0wg","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"* Ferumoxytol (Feraheme®)","guid":"qb5cCoQVonjky8PSqBoR7A","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"13","text":"* LMWID (INFED®/Cosmofer®)","guid":"eHe6JUZHv9hqUwAPDeE7JA","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"13","text":"* FDI (Monoferric®/Monofer®)","guid":"CyLbe2Ki85rPW6-X9mX9eA","children":[]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"10","text":"* **Subóptimas\\N(para TDI):**","guid":"JkLaMD321BmbRUgF_GEmow","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"* Ferumoxytol Genérico","guid":"n8g0unxVdH5AnEUSLx1QWQ","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"* FCM (Injectafer®/Ferinject®)","guid":"r3O_jiphQBqvwopjFDzLmA","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"17","text":"* Sucrosa de Hierro","guid":"Hew9YZlgkoKCc4NiH2A4vQ","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"17","text":"* Gluconato Férrico","guid":"78XpoyVOCUZpvWGv3fo3Eg","children":[]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"10","text":"* **Detalles\\NFormulaciones TDI:**","guid":"YiWz7OqF0hSptS-E7jFGZg","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"* **LMWID:**","guid":"L6XCe1oyJz2VsME6FOXnDw","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"* Dosis/Tiempo Rec.: 1000 mg / 60 min (en 250 mL SN).","guid":"IApQvxnL3CG28tpbDpDWsQ","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"23","text":"* Monitorización FDA: Inicio lento o test 25 mg.","guid":"3UuT0LF793fnGLrjrkYxrQ","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"23","text":"* Nota: Etiqueta 100 mg es subóptima.","guid":"sGMDnkXEeFeaW7o3jCjLXA","children":[]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"22","text":"* **Ferumoxytol:**","guid":"eMtN4MMqhq1d9_pdsr6Fcw","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"* Dosis/Tiempo Rec.: 1020 mg / 30 min (en 100 mL SN) (si seguro permite).","guid":"cMsOHNId5747Ct_rDDIgMA","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"27","text":"* Precaución: Interferencia MRI (<8 sem); iniciar lento.","guid":"EEfWOZviCi2DUO51KkT8yg","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"27","text":"* Nota: Etiqueta 510 mg x 2 es actual pero TDI estudiada.","guid":"4Ke_UvT4G8vmE8rsjP79Pg","children":[]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"22","text":"* **Ferumoxytol\\NGenérico:**","guid":"GHOZmF_FB_75ivTSwgbglw","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"* Precaución: Sin datos publicados; doble reacción vs marca (datos FDA); posible sustitución farmacia.","guid":"4aMGkhgnUFxLNE-AWysD8A","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"31","text":"* Administración: Igual que marca por ahora.","guid":"wznQwGIougNU_Jh0HSoB-g","children":[]}]},{"id":"34","parent":"22","text":"* **FCM:**","guid":"hZfZsabZ_lUcV4KPFwWpGQ","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"* Dosis/Tiempo: 750 mg (vial EE. UU.) / 20-30 min (en 100 mL SN); 1000 mg (Europa).","guid":"et95HIyKHNGt_W-Y_JDXNA","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"34","text":"* Problemas: Requiere ≥1500 mg o desperdicio (EE.UU.); **Alto riesgo TE-HP** (evitar si repetición).","guid":"tExL53H1XUTZkVRMPITTbg","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"22","text":"* **FDI:**","guid":"uf50huVWSvo0E4uSdI0-rA","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"* Dosis/Tiempo: 1000 mg (o 20 mg/kg, máx 1500 mg) / ≥20 min (en 100 mL SN).","guid":"25I3yp1vWM0vAz7xxChoTA","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"* Ventaja: Única con etiqueta FDA para TDI; menor riesgo TE-HP vs FCM.","guid":"nD0aViyXh3YBfWFCgzNXCw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"10","text":"* **Frecuencia\\NAdministración:**","guid":"ZRzFTtPMQz_oi11ihyD4Xg","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"* Depende de causa ID (eliminada vs. continua/malabsorción).","guid":"ESAyOmu8rfma_vw5iP2aBw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"0","text":"## 3. Monitorización\\Nde Laboratorio","guid":"","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"* **Cuándo:** 4-8 semanas post-última infusión.","guid":"5ljXRYR-yAjAVY5XR_FPVw","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"42","text":"* **Qué:** CBC, Ferritina, TSAT.","guid":"VswXY1F-1_kXbfpWI5VvVw","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"42","text":"* **Meta:** Ferritina ≥ 50 ng/mL (sin inflamación).","guid":"1OzaXaKTKCOsNeTwqi940g","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"42","text":"* **Consideraciones:**","guid":"fsEzy1c7WpkSzJCBIh73GQ","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"* Inflamación: Puede ↑ Ferritina (falso normal), TSAT < 20% más fiable para ID.","guid":"58HvvoMhDHkfQGkV2HoFXg","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"* Tests Alternativos (limitados): sTfR, CHr/RET-He.","guid":"L1TNsTcdeug4vurcLSk1JA","children":[]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"42","text":"* **Frecuencia:** Según causa y riesgo recurrencia ID.","guid":"dJxBUR6cbu92qdS0aBWE3w","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"42","text":"* **Embarazo:**","guid":"v4eD8tw4wugLQ_Wrf9pdZw","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"* Evitar < 13 sem gestación.","guid":"KdEBrCc-X-Q__Ry4WVWCJQ","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"* Administración/Formulaciones: Seguras (igual no embarazadas).","guid":"faP5B4yJxXL8pzqqIxLfiQ","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"50","text":"* Monitorización fetal: No requerida.","guid":"cko7TBNsaeKYuEQDrJvHvA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"0","text":"## 4. Reacciones: Infusión\\N(CARPA) vs. Alérgica (IgE)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"* **CARPA\\N(Más común):**","guid":"7hl-xjEtez-GDRHNT6nChg","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"* Mecanismo: Activación complemento por hierro lábil/nanopartícula.","guid":"i4mKVsWfiourG-kgrCBPVA","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"55","text":"* Características: No IgE, no sensibilización previa, inicio rápido, autolimitada.","guid":"VoZE0jUl7Ormko5uYW-Fwg","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"55","text":"* Síntomas: Flushing, mialgias, dolor espalda/pecho (SIN anafilaxia).","guid":"ORzUD1hV08zbrwRdcW53_A","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"55","text":"* Factores: Estabilidad formulación, velocidad infusión.","guid":"OIEa9AxDSfGZSTvwmlU-rQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"54","text":"* **Alérgica\\N(Rara):**","guid":"8Cw3frUKytWtoOoURkiynA","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"* Mecanismo: IgE mediada, requiere sensibilización.","guid":"U_3DjknPHdoxOG6Yz5IZYw","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"* Características: Sistémica, amenaza la vida.","guid":"2kPZpNDP71hX6tUvfINQDw","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"60","text":"* Síntomas: Anafilaxia (compromiso vía aérea, hipotensión, etc.).","guid":"ZMMz1ruCEoLc0UrEsXPfEQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"0","text":"## 5. Manejo de\\NReacciones de Infusión","guid":"","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"* **Preparación:** Educación personal y paciente.","guid":"H9K9LxVFsgxh8Hm0pgqRNA","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"* **Premedicación:** Controversial; considerar en alto riesgo; *evitar H1 1ª gen*.","guid":"5R6hDn6nPMd8ZTXrpyGhIg","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"64","text":"* **Acción Inmediata (Cualquier reacción):** **DETENER INFUSIÓN**, evaluar, KVO con SN.","guid":"3kqjdMh2JPAtKh3A_gS_RA","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"64","text":"* **Manejo\\NLeve/Moderada:**","guid":"Ybesb_o-OiWgrZIridaifg","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"* Monitorizar ≥ 15 min.","guid":"uKv9R9_R8EsElGM8xRAdFQ","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"68","text":"* Tratamiento sintomático (Antiemético, Antihistamínico H2 2ª gen).","guid":"_BXdt_c1oiJcNuOLrnaL0Q","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"68","text":"* Si no mejora: Considerar Corticosteroide IV.","guid":"9hozM0vGsnwV5Hi5kzeHww","children":[]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"64","text":"* **Re-exposición:** Posible si resolución completa, reiniciar a 50% tasa.","guid":"jLffzPNbe01BqjTBBCRr1w","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"64","text":"* **Manejo\\NSevera/Anafilaxia:**","guid":"5VFgvUwz-Ybz16r7EN-66Q","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"* Emergencia: Llamar ayuda, Epinefrina IM, O2, etc. (protocolo anafilaxia).","guid":"g4k1emAdcrPyuPFlBKZZDg","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"* **Post-Infusión:**","guid":"EZRdUVOysq_2WgqD_Df8hg","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"* Observación 30 min: No necesaria.","guid":"szEuZDJ75oon0AmJVaylSw","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"* Educar: Reacciones tardías (tipo gripe, AINEs).","guid":"iFTIPNNMoOoR_KNLJcQc_w","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"75","text":"* **Reporte:** Documentar detalles (severidad, tiempo, manejo, etc.).","guid":"Wlc5vb7WiiG5wwEz9qAmrg","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"0","text":"## 6. Hipofosfatemia\\NEmergente del Tratamiento\\N(TE-HP)","guid":"k4Ak02USHyNbPctDlrYJrw","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"* **Qué es:** ↓ Fosfato sérico post-hierro IV (primeras 2 sem).","guid":"KXNEp2--3sV7CjfrjPR-SQ","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"* **Riesgo Mayor:** **FCM** (Incidencia 47-75%, puede ser severa/prolongada).","guid":"lAizBUNCpE39J4x-PCeP-w","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"79","text":"* **Riesgo Menor:** LMWID, Ferumoxytol, FDI (<10%).","guid":"wJc84gQbmMQ1B-RdmK-MSQ","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"79","text":"* **Mecanismo:** ↑ iFGF23 → Pérdida renal P → ↓ Vit D activa → Hiperpara 2º → Riesgo óseo.","guid":"384N15JyWZxCDrnTmsjEkA","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"79","text":"* **Factores Riesgo:** FCM, infusiones repetidas, función renal normal, ID severa.","guid":"OBbaQk3thbKVsB0dVXagog","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"79","text":"* **Síntomas:** Fatiga, debilidad, dolor óseo (similares a ID).","guid":"Km9hgRd-7goFJyYnPlZD5A","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"79","text":"* **Manejo:**","guid":"BBL8Yw4dMXDJcQJfFqEOIw","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"* **NO suplementar Fosfato.**","guid":"8WT4rmPtHX0nwZBlmmwz6g","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"86","text":"* Tratar hiperparatiroidismo 2º (ej. Vit D).","guid":"I2ccPHKpWphASn0AQMtKkQ","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"86","text":"* **Cesar FCM** si es la causa.","guid":"JnoZNd1abXnvFuMAXZ6Ofg","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"86","text":"* Observar si leve/asintomática.","guid":"Fi070Gu3WSW8qD35GJ549Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"79","text":"* **Monitorización:**","guid":"-k_UAGFcjVtPIejLxYXIRA","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"* **FCM:** Mandatoria en riesgo / repetición / <3 meses entre cursos.","guid":"jV3k8U_gU-_GSARrzgiv4Q","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"91","text":"* **FDI:** Basada en síntomas; HP prolongada no reportada.","guid":"6AE2-7sN897UKxMeZoo1jQ","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"91","text":"* Evaluar dolor óseo con imágenes.","guid":"h41iaIQQNiKEuk2b_QFetA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"0","text":"## 7. Resumen","guid":"","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"* Hierro IV: Seguro y eficaz para diversas causas de ID/IDA.","guid":"f5ivAgNRK6Sq4qhkoAqVdA","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"95","text":"* Reacciones graves: Raras.","guid":"9KvKf5zI9J4EDFGCGIFtIA","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"95","text":"* Guía: Fomenta mejores prácticas para maximizar seguridad y eficacia.","guid":"QlPP02W8N5S1bpJ-J0nnFw","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":98,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Hematología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Hematología","filename":"Paper. Guía hierro EV-2025-1","id":"map_1072","resolved_references":[]}